<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Successful - NovaGems</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #008080; /* Teal */
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #e6f7f7;
      border: 1px solid #008080;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .info p {
      margin: 6px 0;
      color: #004d4d;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #cceaea;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #008080;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .total {
      text-align: right;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>üéâ Payment Successful!</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>
      Your payment for order <strong>#{{orderId}}</strong> has been successfully completed.
    </p>

    <div class="info">
      <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> {{currency}} {{amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
    </div>

    <h3>üõçÔ∏è Purchased Items:</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Product</th>
          <th>Quantity</th>
          <th>Price</th>
          <th>Subtotal</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each items}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{this.name}}</td>
          <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
          <td>{{this.price}}</td>
          <td>{{this.subtotal}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p class="total">Total Paid: <strong>{{currency}} {{amount}}</strong></p>

    <p>
      Thank you for shopping with <strong>NovaGems</strong>!  
      Your items will be processed shortly, and we‚Äôll notify you once your order is shipped.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© {{year}} NovaGems | All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
